Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:21.86,STAFF,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻译: 凉菜 Leader  校对: Potianwu  润稿：ATM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:19.90,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#5  顾问！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.10,0:24:19.60,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}#6         学园祭！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真热
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到个有趣的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么东东啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前澪翻出来的纸箱里发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是以前轻音部的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好强悍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人不禁想问「这是那个年代的乐队？」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我居然觉得「乐队」就应该是这种印象…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个部分要不要改一下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指头的皮磨破了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  看着就够疼的了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪你也看看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到听不到  看不到听不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  我也因为鼓敲过头了手上水泡破掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律啊  有没有创可贴啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  稍微借一下谱架…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们两个帮忙把笔记拿过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消毒水渗进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  手指不要动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好整齐的桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个硬度的话皮很快还会破的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样重复几次之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等指头上的皮变硬之后弹吉它就不会痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都要过这一关的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样子的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  老师弹过吉他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊  以前朋友有弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  要不要来杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师人好好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是觉得她人长得好漂亮啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  佐和子老师是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你刚才去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小澪拜托我去申请学园祭期间的舞台使用许可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是轻音部还没有被认可为正式社团
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这样啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有被认可为正式社团？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是凑齐四个部员就万事大吉的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按理说应该是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说回来  我们还没被正式认可…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么随便用音乐教室会不会不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然到现在也没有人说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么问题吧…应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个还是先去问问事情的原委吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来澪她人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪的话  人还在那儿抖着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是部长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是唯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  小和为啥在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥…我是学生会的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  不愧是小和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们二位真的是从小一块长大的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然名单里还没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  有什么头绪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这恐怕就是传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将弱小社团逼入废部绝境的…学生会阴谋！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和你可是个纯洁的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点迷途知返
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来社团申请表该不会没交上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团申请表？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我怎么听说过！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时  季节还是春天…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我是部长就由我来写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我带了磅蛋糕来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:51.24,up,NTP,0015,0000,0000,,磅蛋糕：用相等份量，一磅面粉、一磅奶油、一磅糖和八个鸡蛋\N做出來的浓郁重奶油蛋糕，所以叫磅蛋糕(Pound cake)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家开吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  律
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦  吃完了就写啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「知道了啦  吃完了就写啦」…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就写啦」…「写啦」…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道  果然是你个猪头…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  小律她也不是故意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬不能这么护着她啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢  轻音部还真适合唯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你们没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来想想办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻…音…部…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部员四名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…顾问呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顾问？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山中佐和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为本校的音乐老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因其美丽的容貌及和蔼的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅是学生  也深受老师们的喜爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:08:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此  在乐器的演奏和演唱方面也颇有造诣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人气之高拥有粉丝团也不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始在说些什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请当轻音部的顾问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来还没找到顾问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只有求助于老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  虽然我也很愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已经是吹奏部的顾问了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以兼任的话可能有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止前来搭讪的男性不计其数…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就算给我戴高帽也不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会耽误您很多时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习的话我们会自己安排
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在这里签字画押就行了  够简单了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盯——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师是本校毕业生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才看了一下以前轻音部的相册
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相…相册是放在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在活动室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到  那最后一本居然会保存在这个学校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是绝不可公布于世的  沾满鲜血的历史…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是万不可唤醒的恶魔之子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可窥视的封印之书…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可打开的禁断之门…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  就是这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被你们看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我就是传说中的轻音部前部员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子们  正等着你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHUT UP
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放啦  好难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不见听不见…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没走出阴影啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那吉他也应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦  弹一下弹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来嘛来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印解除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:11:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这由桃花心木和岩枫木制成的Les Paul独有的质感…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:11:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}{\an7}桃花心木：红色硬木  主要用于制造高档家具、乐器和游艇、高档汽车等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:11:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}{\an7}岩枫：高级木材之一  重量适中  有弹性  坚韧结实  不易萎缩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:11:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}{\an7}Les Paul：1952年由Gibson推出的电吉他  与Stratocaster齐名的经典型号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hum-bucking的拾音器发出的甜美的泛音…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}{\an7}Hum-bucking：在拾音器中用于减低噪音的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}{\an7}拾音器：捕捉弦的振动并将其转化为电子信号的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}{\an7}泛音：指声音中除了基频外其他频率的音  基音和不同泛音的能量比例是决定音色的核心因素
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就没办法了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼神都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速弹?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点弦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:24.97,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点弦：不用匹克或手指弹拨  而直接靠手指用力点击琴弦而发出声响的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙弹吉他?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的吉他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个把音乐教室当什么地方了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才都看见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当老师之后决定当个淑女的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个发生在八年前的故事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然开始讲上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更喜欢狂野一点的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成为他所喜欢的那种女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得更加狂野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加…更加狂野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加…更加…更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂野  狂野  更狂野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你交往也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是那么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用安慰我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  抬起头来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让别人知道的话就做我们的顾问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  真够强势
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  好像呆呆的  感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…就是这种感觉的原创曲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  从顾问的角度来看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节奏赶旋律拖的问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节奏凌乱不和谐啊等等许多问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是首先是…  没有主唱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道连歌词也还没写…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你们还想在学园祭的舞台上演出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占领音乐教室以来一直在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可不是喝茶的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来个…蛋糕怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就不客气了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先写词就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子老师做了我们的顾问后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎么的心怦怦跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油填词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心怦怦跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看  让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就看了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么就不就的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  还是很难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  又不会笑你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来了就是想让我们看的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一下下  悄悄地让我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看的话当然是我先看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说为什么  因为我是部长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:16:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  我就是小澪的心灵挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就是小澪的心灵挚友2号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没大没小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是澪的心灵故乡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候变成我故乡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  乡下的奶奶还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这和刚才的话没关系的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  去年有寄贺年卡去吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别岔开话题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord2\blur3}一看到你心总是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord2\blur3}扑通扑通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord2\blur3}悸动的心情像棉花糖一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord2\blur3}轻轻飘飘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒  彻底败了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我个人来说感觉还是写得不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是和印象有天壤之别…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  小唯  你也说两句
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这歌词我很喜欢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬觉得怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超陶醉的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬也很中意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和酱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和酱觉得这歌词不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们3个再稍微重新考虑下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先大家要冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说喜欢这种嗲声嗲气的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许能提升我的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师真是年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是佐和子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟定佐和子老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…也觉得这歌词不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就用这歌词上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么澪就当主唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因…因为  因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样难为情的歌词唱不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  作者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪不行的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬要要试试看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是弹键盘就竭尽全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样啊  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  要试试看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  人家又不是那么擅长唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道能不能胜任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我说谎了  我要唱  我想唱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就唱来听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到你心总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要边弹吉他边唱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是那样啊  我都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是忘记唱歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹吉他的时候唱不了歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师帮你做特训
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就首先教你牙弹吉他的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟紧了  不过注意别被当做坏孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬她啊…难不成对佐和子老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对佐和子老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬  你喜欢佐和子老师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  只是觉得大家都是女孩子真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人觉得可以的话  不是挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…演唱者是小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲目是「轻飘飘时间」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  那么演出时间定下来后再联络你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你特地跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是学生会的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小唯真的没有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从上周开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后就到佐和子老师家进行特训
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概能赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧小唯  让她们见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进步了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自信满溢的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到你心总是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扑通扑通
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音哑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.97,0:21:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装可爱也没用！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…那主唱…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换人的话就今天哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪的话肯定记得歌词
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作词者本人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离正式演出还有3天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.55,0:23:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂小律  要进行正式演出前的练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  现在不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:24:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那离演出还有一段时间  不练习下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  来练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有  什么都没有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.19,0:24:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就是正式演出吧？好好练习下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.47,0:24:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.87,0:24:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习啊…
